{"tid":2222510,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中國留學生稱傷害世界和平 教授用「中國病毒」字眼被休假","createTime":"2020-09-29T06:50:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-29T06:50:02.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"27fe66a29fdce58232a8faf193533d3092e6f638","tid":2222510,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T06:50:02.000Z","msg":"（北美通訊）美國辛辛那提大學（ University of Cincinnati）一名來自中國的國際學生表示，對於校內一名教授以種族歧視字眼「中國病毒」（ Chinese Virus ）來形容武漢肺炎病毒，感到很受傷，認為會令不知情的人對中國人民產生不好的印象，損害友好交流和全世界的和平。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20200929/67UAOJX3KRFVRP7DBJGX7EWBGA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200929%2F67UAOJX3KRFVRP7DBJGX7EWBGA%2F&d=3%2F9Bgz%2Fikyxb3M9FpachXPFndj8FUwf2P%2BvTNEmbS2k%3D&h=e8d1884f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200929%2F67UAOJX3KRFVRP7DBJGX7EWBGA%2F&h=2059fb63\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20200929/67UAOJX3KRFVRP7DBJGX7EWBGA/</a>"}]}